## 9. 系统流程总览

### 9.1 正常决策系统流程

```text
User Input
  ├── Stock Code
  ├── Natural Language Strategy
  └── Position Settings
        ↓
Strategy Parser / Strategy Loader
        ↓
Market Data Provider
        ↓
Trading Guardian Agent
        ↓
Policy Evaluator
        ↓
Risk Checker
        ↓
Trading Decision
        ↓
Behavior Logger
        ↓
Proof Metadata Builder
        ↓
Stable JSON Hashing
        ↓
Proof Hash
        ↓
Injective Anchor / Mock Anchor
        ↓
Verifier
        ↓
Verified Alert
```

---

### 9.2 Proof 生成流程

```text
Agent Profile
        ↓
agentProfileHash

User Strategy
        ↓
strategyHash

Market Snapshot
        ↓
marketDataHash

Behavior Log
        ↓
behaviorLogHash

Trading Decision Output
        ↓
outputHash

agentProfileHash
+ strategyHash
+ marketDataHash
+ behaviorLogHash
+ outputHash
        ↓
Final Proof Hash
```

---

### 9.3 Verifier 验证流程

```text
读取 proof metadata
        ↓
重新计算 agentProfileHash
        ↓
重新计算 strategyHash
        ↓
重新计算 marketDataHash
        ↓
重新计算 behaviorLogHash
        ↓
重新计算 outputHash
        ↓
重新计算 final proofHash
        ↓
对比记录中的 proofHash
        ↓
检查 forbidden inputs
        ↓
检查策略和风控结果
        ↓
检查 Injective anchor
        ↓
输出 PASSED / REJECTED
```

---

### 9.4 Injective Anchor 流程

```text
生成 proof hash
        ↓
构造 memo
        ↓
写入 Injective testnet transaction memo
        ↓
获得 tx hash
        ↓
前端展示 tx hash / explorer link
        ↓
verifier 检查 proof 与链上锚点是否一致
```

